<div3>
<poem><comhd3><idref>Z300646979</idref><collection>1 2</collection>

<somhead><somauth>Bell, Henry Thomas Mackenzie, 1856-1930<sombiog>5165</sombiog></somauth> <mainhead>&ldquo;THE COMRADE IN WHITE.&rdquo;</mainhead> <attbytes>4Kb</attbytes><volhead>Poetical Pictures of the Great War. Suitable for Recitation. First Series ... Second Series ... Third Series ... Fourth Series. By Mackenzie Bell (1917&ndash;1918)</volhead></somhead><reflink></reflink><comcitn><TY>DATA</TY><ID>Z300646979</ID><A1>Bell, Henry Thomas Mackenzie, 1856-1930</A1><T1>&ldquo;THE COMRADE IN WHITE.&rdquo;</T1><PBL>T. Fisher Unwin</PBL><Y1>1886</Y1><T2>Poetical Pictures of the Great War. Suitable for Recitation. First Series ... Second Series ... Third Series ... Fourth Series. By Mackenzie Bell (1917&ndash;1918)</T2><T3>Literature Online</T3></comcitn></comhd3>
