<div2><comhd2><idref>Z200646988</idref><collection>1 2</collection>

Third Series. <attbytes>16Kb</attbytes><reflink></reflink><comcitn><TY>BOOK</TY><ID>Z200646988</ID><A1>Bell, Henry Thomas Mackenzie, 1856-1930</A1><T1>Poetical Pictures of the Great War. Suitable for Recitation. First Series ... Second Series ... Third Series ... Fourth Series. By Mackenzie Bell (1917&ndash;1918)</T1><PBL>T. Fisher Unwin</PBL><Y1>1886</Y1><T2>Literature Online</T2></comcitn></comhd2>

